      "id": "give_up_hoping",
      "text": "Stop wanting things",
      "description": "If you don't reach, you can't fall.",
      "resultText": "You make a conscious decision to stop having ambitions. Every goal you've ever set has led to disappointment, so why continue the cycle? You retreat into the bare minimum, doing only what's necessary to survive. The resignation brings a dark kind of relief—if you expect nothing, you can't be disappointed. But the world becomes flatter, grayer. You're safe from failure because you've stopped trying.",
