      "text": "Figure out what went wrong",
      "description": "Failure is information, not destiny.",
      "resultText": "Through the pain, you force yourself to examine the wreckage objectively. What was in your control? What wasn't? What can you learn? The analysis doesn't erase the hurt, but it transforms the failure from a condemnation into data. You identify genuine mistakes you made, but also factors beyond your control. Your ambition is diminished but not destroyed. You're learning how to fail without being broken by it.",
